# <type>(<scope>): <description>
#
# Types:  feat  fix  refactor  test  docs  chore  perf  ci  build
#
# Scopes: peering  transport  ipc  security  topology  input
#         config   cli        daemon  discovery  planning
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Body (what changed and why — not how; wrap at 72 chars):



# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Footers:
#
#   BREAKING CHANGE: <description>      ← breaking changes
#   Phase: <N> | Plan: <name>           ← .planning/ commits only
#   Co-Authored-By: Name <email>        ← human co-authors
#   Model: <model-id>                   ← AI-authored commits (best-effort)
#
# Examples:
#   feat(security): implement Ed25519 keypair generation
#   fix(topology): correct monitor offset calculation for non-zero origins
#   docs(planning): update ROADMAP.md after phase 1 completion
#   refactor(transport): extract framing logic into dedicated module
